                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation of natural lithium metallic target",
                " (4.0 mg/cm2 thick, 1.0x1.0 cm2, energy loss in the",
                "  half thickness of ~120 keV) by protons at 4.0, 4.5",
                "  and 5.0 MeV.",
                " Neutron energy spread due to finite opening angle of",
                "  neutron emission (+/-14 deg) is ~100 keV."
              ]
            }
